snippet.title: Spectacular Sparky Announcement Trailer (Nintendo Switch/Steam/Epic)
snippet.description: A video-game mascot with 16-bit attitude, Spectacular Sparky is coming to Nintendo Switch, Steam and the Epic Games Store on October 20! Wishlist today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1300100/Spectacular_Sparky/
